ol.li:
The equation 4x^2+y=0 is equivalent to
        y=-4x^2 ~~~~~~ \text{or} ~~~~~~ y= \dfrac{-x^2}{\dfrac{1}{4}}   
    The graph is a parabola that opens downward.

